<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Request for Verification of Employment Reference</title>
    {{> meta}}
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color: #F0E8E1; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          {{> header}}
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="background-color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #EAEBED; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 12px; max-width: 600px;">
            <tr>
              <td>
                <h1 style="font-size: 24px; color: #3A3131; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 20px; line-height: 1.3;">Request for Verification of Employment Reference</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #3A3131; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Dear {{clientName}},</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #3A3131; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                  I am reaching out on behalf of Norland Agency. We are currently assisting
                  <strong>{{nannyFirstName}} {{nannyLastName}}</strong> in securing a new position.
                  As part of our standard process, we are seeking to confirm the details of the
                  reference they have provided regarding their period of employment with you.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #3A3131; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                  Please click the 'Verify Reference' button below to review and confirm the details of the reference.
                </p>

                <a href="{{returnUrl}}" style="display: block; background-color: #3A3131; color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 8px; width: 300px;text-align: center; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Verify Reference</a>

                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #3A3131; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
                  If you have any additional comments or concerns regarding {{nannyFirstName}}'s performance
                  or employment history, please do not hesitate to share them with me directly.
                </p>

                <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #3A3131; margin: 0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.5;">Best regards,</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;">Norland Agency</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          {{> footer}}
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
